---
title: Chicken, Bacon & Basil Mayo Sandwiches with Tomato Salad & Balsamic Dipper
description: This is far from “just another chicken sandwich,” and here’s why: bacon is very much involved! You’ll build these chicken-and-bacon champs on toasted flatbread spread with creamy basil aioli and herbaceous tomato salad. Serve your sumptuous sammies with a side of tangy balsamic dipping sauce to take this classic concept right over the top!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/659d969a145e14b9dce0905a-1040383e.jpeg
